headline: Consumers Energy Will Carry out Upgrades to Improve Electric Reliability
summary: Consumers Energy will move forward with an aggressive plan to clear trees near power lines and strengthen the grid to deliver energy to nearly 2 million homes and businesses, under spending approved today to support the company's Reliability Roadmap.
